data.description: Seller Offering 10K concession  Experience modern luxury with this newly-renovated 5-bedroom, 2-full bath split level sanctuary. Every detail has been meticulously updated to provide both comfort and aesthetic delight.    *Recent Upgrades & Features:*    *2021 Enhancements:*  - Newly installed pavers around the pool.  - Outdoor Tiki bar installation.  - Brand new water tank - enjoy pure well water with no water bill.  - Converted man cave for your relaxation and entertainment.  - Brand new driveway adds both functionality and curb appeal.    *2022 Upgrades:*  - Massive Private Backyard with a refurbished in-ground pool surrounded by new deck and concrete.  - Energy-efficient solar panel installation for electricity bill savings.  - New roof safeguards your home against the elements.  - Fresh skylight windows brightening your living space.  - Retainer wall installation for enhanced landscaping.  - Yard leveling ensures a smooth and even outdoor space.  - Recessed lighting installed throughout, creating a bright and welcoming ambiance.  - Brand new fence installed securing your private oasis.  - Inviting and impressive new entry door.    *2023 Additions:*  - Basketball court for the sport enthusiast.  - Freshly painted deck, perfect for outdoor relaxation.  - Brand new furnace circuit for consistent comfort.  - Lifetime septic tank promises longevity and peace of mind with no need for annual waste movement.    Additional features include the attic storage space and the new HVAC system installed in 2021, ensuring optimal comfort throughout the seasons.    Top-to-bottom, this home has been revamped with care and precision, guaranteeing the new owner a residence of utmost quality. Don't let this opportunity slip by. Book a viewing today!
